Command: show
Description: Displays information about the current session and environment.

Usage:
    show                - List all currently set dynamic variables.
    show details        - Display specific details for the active exploit.
    show aliases        - List all configured command aliases.
    show shells         - Display available system shells from /etc/shells.
    show <VAR1> <VAR2>  - Show the value of specific variables (e.g., 'show R_HOST').